title: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Waterways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Sachsen-Anhalt Waterways, Germany, 2008
description: This data, provided by Openstreetmaps, shows various waterways in the Sachsen-Anhalt administrative area in the country of Germany. Waterways include canals, rivers, streams, and other water bound transportation routes. Data was uploaded as a poly line shape file with attributes for Feature name, feature type, and feature width when available.
